<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「中國共產主義青年團」</span></span>（中國共青團／共青團）<br />\n中國共產主義青年團申請人的加入年齡必須介於14歲至28歲間[4]，共青團同時還主導和監督以14歲以下兒童組成的先鋒組織中國少年先鋒隊[2]。<span style=\"color: teal;\">截至2017年年底，全國共有共青團員8124.6萬名，其中學生團員5795.1萬名；共有基層團組織357.9萬個，其中，基層團委20.4萬個，基層團工委1.6萬個，團總支16.5萬個，團支部319.4萬個，[5]成為世界上規模最大的青年組織之一</span>。<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/中國共產主義青年團\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%B1%E7%94%A2%E4%B8%BB%E7%BE%A9%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E5%9C%98&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDbzBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=a2270bba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/中國共產主義青年團</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XOENCD6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXOENCD6.png&h=3f236ba8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ytgkdcq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYtgkdcq.png&h=29148297&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x2Oyyc0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx2Oyyc0.jpg&h=c64a4576&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nRGTx1F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnRGTx1F.jpg&h=c494c605&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「童心向党　健康成长」</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣由六歲去到廿八歲</span>，<br />\n咁你話深唔深紅（深藍絲）？</span>"},{"pid":"a16ff00ad5b97a9963e07a5f5664ab2c6b676480","tid":1461744,"uid":63124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"051e4443a14a72e11014911284d3a0bf19368788","tid":1461744,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5c66c0400d69d050ced722c864876771ddfbadf","tid":1461744,"uid":63124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:23:44.000Z","